Popular Nollywood actor Kenneth Okolie is one of the hottest, most handsome Nigerian known. The young gentleman who is a former Mr Nigeria went off the singles market just as soon as he married his US-based girlfriend Jessica on December 16, 2017. As it appears, the couple recently celebrated their one year anniversary. Indeed, how time flies! Kenneth Okolie could not keep his excitement in as his marriage with his wife clocked one year. In expressing his excitement, he took to his page to share a lovely picture of them together. In the photos he shared, the former Mr Nigeria was in a passionate hug with his sweetheart. Evidently, his life has been all the better with her by his side. Alongside the photos he posted, the guy also shared a caption which was all the merrier in describing his innate emotional feelings for his wife of one year.